msgid "I just need to open my locker, and then the closet to end this."
msgstr "我只需要打开我的储物柜，然后打开衣柜就可以结束这一切。"

msgid "My locker is..."
msgstr "我的储物柜是..."

msgid "It's pretty obvious, isn't it?"
msgstr "很明显，不是么？"

msgid "This isn't your locker."
msgstr "这不是你的储物柜。"

msgid "A locker."
msgstr "储物柜。"

msgid "Huh? What's that red thing? It's the first time I see it."
msgstr "啊？这个红色的东西是什么？这我还是第一次见到。"

msgid "There's nothing else to see here."
msgstr "这里已经没有其他能看的了。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Trash fills your locker."
msgstr "垃圾堆满了你的储物柜。"

msgid "What a mess."
msgstr "真是一团糟啊。"

msgid "\"Welcome back, Lacie."
msgstr "“欢迎回来，莱西。"

msgid "We've missed you at school."
msgstr "我们在学校很想念你。"

msgid "You'll have a lot to catch up on, so your classmates organized the reading material for you."
msgstr "你还有很多进度要赶，所以你的同学们为你准备了阅读材料。"

msgid "You can find it in your locker."
msgstr "你可以在你的储物柜里找到。"

msgid "Please be sure to look over everything carefully."
msgstr "请务必仔细查看所有内容。"

msgid "You wouldn't want to fail the year.\""
msgstr "你也不想辜负这一年的努力吧。”"

msgid "...sigh."
msgstr "...哎。"

msgid "...Blah blah blah."
msgstr "...巴拉巴拉巴拉。"

msgid "It's always the same text."
msgstr "永远是一样的文字。"

msgid "The note will be back in this spot next time, even if I crumple it."
msgstr "即使我把这张纸揉成一团，下次它也会恢复原样。"

msgid "Peace and quiet."
msgstr "安静了。"

msgid "Nah, it's better like this."
msgstr "不，这样更好。"

msgid "...Heh... never gets old."
msgstr "...哈哈...永远都不会改变。"

msgid "Pick up ${item:global.reditem_1}?"
msgstr "要捡起${item:global.reditem_1}吗？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "It's the exit."
msgstr "这就是出口了。"

msgid "It doesn't open until I check the locker..."
msgstr "在我检查储物柜之前，它是不会开启的..."

msgid "Blindingly white light is all you can see."
msgstr "你所能看见的只有刺眼的白光。"

msgid "Students, laughing at you."
msgstr "正在嘲笑你的同学们。"

msgid "...I hate them."
msgstr "...我讨厌他们。"

msgid "The passageway has closed behind you."
msgstr "你身后的通道已经关上了。"
